  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n商工相、復興院総裁、阪急電鉄社長"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"02k.html\">一覧　（カ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%259E%2597%2520%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25B8%2589\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　山梨県出身。慶応義塾卒業後、三井銀行に入行。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　箕面有馬電気軌道（のちの阪急急行電鉄）の創立に参画、専務となる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　路線を拡大して田舎電車を屈指の電鉄会社に育てた。のち社長、さらに会長。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　宝塚の少女唱歌隊を宝塚少女歌劇団に、また、阪急ビルのマーケットを阪急百貨店にする。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　東京宝塚劇場を設立、日劇、帝劇を合併し、東宝を創立する。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦後、東宝の再建を果たし、またコマ劇場を大阪・梅田と東京・新宿に設立。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
